  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A health coaching intervention in those with pre-disease (pre-hypertension or pre-diabetes)
      but without pre-existing cardiovascular disease will effectively help participants change
      their lifestyle behaviour and prevent or delay onset of cardiovascular disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
